OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774995068
OL,3,CScott Mills was investigated for
OL,4,C'serious sexual offences' against teen
OL,5,Cunder 16
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police said Tuesday
OL,8,Fthat BBC Radio DJ Scott Mills was
OL,9,Finvestigated in 2016 in relation to
OL,10,Falleged "serious sexual offences
OL,11,Fagainst a teenage boy", telling ITV
OL,12,FNews the victim was under 16.
OL,14,FA Met police spokesperson said they
OL,15,Fcouldn't confirm the specific age of
OL,16,Fthe victim due to the risk of jigsaw
OL,17,Fidentification.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774995068
OL,3,CScott Mills was investigated for
OL,4,C'serious sexual offences' against teen
OL,5,Cunder 16
OL,7,FThe revelation comes after Mills was
OL,8,Freportedly sacked from his BBC Radio 2
OL,9,Fjob on Monday over allegations
OL,10,Frelating to "personal conduct".
OL,12,FMills has not publicly commented and
OL,13,Fwas last on air on Tuesday last week.
OL,15,FThe Metropolitan Police told ITV News
OL,16,F: "In December 2016, the Met began an
OL,17,Finvestigation following a referral
OL,18,Ffrom another police force.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
