PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774995068
OL,3,CScott Mills was investigated for
OL,4,C'serious sexual offences' against teen
OL,5,Cunder 16
OL,7,F"The investigation related to
OL,8,Fallegations of serious sexual offences
OL,9,Fagainst a teenage boy. These were
OL,10,Freported to taken place between 1997
OL,11,Fand 2000.
OL,13,F"As part of these enquiries, a man who
OL,14,Fwas in his 40s at the time of the
OL,15,Finterview, was questioned by police
OL,16,Funder caution in July 2018.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774995068
OL,3,CScott Mills was investigated for
OL,4,C'serious sexual offences' against teen
OL,5,Cunder 16
OL,7,F"A full file of evidence was submitted
OL,8,Fto the Crown Prosecution Service, who
OL,9,Fdetermined the evidential threshold
OL,10,Fhad not been met to bring charges.
OL,11,FFollowing this advice, the
OL,12,Finvestigation was closed in May 2019."
OL,14,FThe Mirror, which initially reported
OL,15,Fthe DJ's sacking, has linked it to the
OL,16,Fpolice investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
