OL,3,CScott Mills was investigated for
OL,4,C'serious sexual offences' against teen
OL,5,Cunder 16
OL,7,FIn a statement, the BBC said: "While
OL,8,Fwe do not comment on matters relating
OL,9,Fto individuals, we can confirm Scott
OL,10,FMills is no longer contracted to work
OL,11,Fwith the BBC".
