OL,3,CScott Mills was investigated for
OL,4,C'serious sexual offences' against teen
OL,5,Cunder 16
OL,7,FIn an internal note to staff on Monday
OL,8,Fmorning, Lorna Clarke, director of
OL,9,Fmusic at the BBC, said: "I wanted to
OL,10,Fpersonally let you know that Scott
OL,11,FMills has left the Breakfast show, and
OL,12,Fthe BBC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
