PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774995068
OL,3,CScott Mills was investigated for
OL,4,C'serious sexual offences' against teen
OL,5,Cunder 16
OL,7,F"I know that this news will be sudden
OL,8,Fand unexpected and therefore must come
OL,9,Fas a shock. Not least as so many of us
OL,10,Fhave worked with Scott over a great
OL,11,Fmany years, across a broad range of
OL,12,Four programmes on R1, 5Live, R2 and
OL,13,FTV. I felt it was important to share
OL,14,Fthis news with you at the earliest
OL,15,Fopportunity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774995068
OL,3,CScott Mills was investigated for
OL,4,C'serious sexual offences' against teen
OL,5,Cunder 16
OL,7,F"Of course, it will also come as a
OL,8,Fshock to our audience and loyal
OL,9,Fbreakfast show listeners too. I will
OL,10,Fupdate everyone with more information
OL,11,Fon plans for the show when I'm able
OL,12,Fto. While I appreciate many of you
OL,13,Fwill have questions, I hope you can
OL,14,Funderstand that I am not going to be
OL,15,Fsaying anything further now."
OL,17,FThe 53-year-old had been working on
OL,18,Fthe breakfast show since taking over
OL,19,Ffrom Zoe Ball in January 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
