OL,3,CScott Mills was investigated for
OL,4,C'serious sexual offences' against teen
OL,5,Cunder 16
OL,7,FMills began his BBC career on Radio 1
OL,8,Fin the late 1990s as the early
OL,9,Fbreakfast host, before going on to
OL,10,Fpresent weekend slots and then an
OL,11,Fearly evening show while providing
OL,12,Fmaternity cover for Sara Cox. When Cox
OL,13,Fdid not return, the programme was
OL,14,Frenamed The Scott Mills Show.
OL,16,FIn 2022, he joined Radio 2, replacing
OL,17,FSteve Wright in his weekday afternoon
OL,18,Fslot.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
